        <Parent_String>Mon (Southeast Asian culture) [300019089], Burmese (culture or style) [300019088], Southeast Asian [300120146], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
